“Hey, you oughta know

even for employees.”{PAUSE}“Must be where they
took {Aeris}.”{PAUSE}“The security's pretty light now.
Alright, let's go!!”

{Tifa}
“Wait a second!
You're not thinking of just going
right through the main entrance, are you?”

{Barret}
“Well what else does it look like!?
I'm gonna kick some Shinra butt and…”

{Tifa}
“That's not going to work!
We've got to find another way…”

{Barret}
“Ain't gonna be no other way!
If we keep wastin' time like this,
{Aeris}'ll…”

{Tifa}
“I know that!
But if we get caught here…”{PAUSE}“Hey, {Cloud}.
…What should we do?”
{CHOICE}Let's bust on in!
{CHOICE}Let's sneak in quietly

{Barret}
“That's more like it!
C'mon, let's go!!”

{Tifa}
“See? Let's be careful and find a
different route!”

“No, no!
The Sister Ray's not this way!”
